OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FSolicitor for the murdered Southport
OL,7,Fvictims Chris White says individuals
OL,8,Fmust be held accountable for failing
OL,9,Fto stop AR from carrying out his
OL,10,Fbrutal attack at a children's dance
OL,11,Fevent.
OL,13,FThe lawyer for the families of three
OL,14,Fgirls murdered in Southport says he
OL,15,Fwill name the individuals who failed
OL,16,Fto prevent the attack if they don't
OL,17,Fsee "clear accountability and real
OL,18,Fchange".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FIt follows a damning report into the
OL,7,Ftragedy which highlights "profound"
OL,8,Fsystemic failures leading up to the
OL,9,Ftragedy which claimed the lives of
OL,10,Fthree young girls.
OL,12,FRepresenting the families of Alice da
OL,13,FSilva Aguiar, Bebe King and Elsie Dot
OL,14,FStancombe, Chris Walker said they are
OL,15,Fliving through a "horror movie" - and
OL,16,Fseeing the extent of the errors in
OL,17,F"black and white" was "devastating."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FHe called for "immediate action",
OL,7,Finsisting that the public deserves
OL,8,Fsystems capable of protecting the
OL,9,Fvulnerable from mass violence.
OL,11,FMr White also added people in local
OL,12,Fauthorities, public agencies and
OL,13,Fpolice who did not take preventative
OL,14,Faction should be sacked - and he will
OL,15,Fpersonally name the individuals if
OL,16,Fthey are not.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FHe said: "We demand disciplinary
OL,7,Fproceedings in relation to the failure
OL,8,Fto implement their internal procedures
OL,9,Fbut also individual failings... and if
OL,10,Fthey've not been concluded to our
OL,11,Fsatisfaction then I will be naming the
OL,12,Findividuals who I believe are most
OL,13,Fculpable.
OL,15,F"I know who they are, and if necessary
OL,16,Fwe will name them, because these
OL,17,Fpeople have to lose their jobs."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
