OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FChairman of the Southport Inquiry Sir
OL,7,FAdrian Fulford published the first
OL,8,Fphase of his findings on Monday,
OL,9,Ffollowing a nine-week public inquiry
OL,10,Fin 2025.
OL,12,FIt found the killer, referred to as
OL,13,FAR, had "clearly revealed" he was an
OL,14,Fextreme danger and his attack on a
OL,15,Fchildren's Taylor Swift themed dance
OL,16,Fclass in Southport on 29 July 2024
OL,17,F"could and should have been prevented".
OL,26,@uD@IOUuD@ZO]yD@AOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FThree girls - Alice da Silva Aguiar,
OL,7,Fnine, Bebe King, six, and Elsie Dot
OL,8,FStancombe, seven - were murdered when
OL,9,Fthe knifeman entered The Hart Space
OL,10,Fand launched his attack.
OL,12,FThe killer, then 17, also attempted to
OL,13,Fmurder eight other children, who
OL,14,Fcannot be named for legal reasons, as
OL,15,Fwell as class instructor Leanne Lucas
OL,16,Fand businessman John Hayes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FThe teenager, jailed for a minimum of
OL,7,F52 years, could have been stopped if
OL,8,Fhis parents had "done what they
OL,9,Fmorally ought to have done", or if
OL,10,Fappropriate arrangements had been put
OL,11,Fin place by agencies to address his
OL,12,Frisk.
OL,14,FChris Walker, a solicitor representing
OL,15,Fthe three bereaved families, welcomed
OL,16,Fthe report but added that "seeing the
OL,17,Fextent of the failures in black and
OL,18,Fwhite is devastating".
OL,26,@pD@QOUqD@[O]xD@[OUzD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FHe said: "The Southport murders were
OL,7,Fnot only predictable, they were
OL,8,Fpreventable. For our families, this
OL,9,Fhas always been about honouring their
OL,10,Fgirls and ensuring no one else endures
OL,11,Fwhat they face every day.
OL,13,F"On behalf of our clients we welcome
OL,14,Fthe report's clear ` though deeply
OL,15,Fdistressing ` findings on the profound
OL,16,Fsystemic failures and individual
OL,17,Ffailures, that preceded this attack
OL,18,Fand the responsibility borne by AR's
OL,19,Fparents."
OL,26,@nD@JOUuD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FMr Walker added that reforms are
OL,7,Frequired urgently.
OL,9,FHe said: "On behalf of the families,
OL,10,Fwe repeat the chair's hope that this
OL,11,Fmarks a genuine turning point.
OL,13,F"This fight does not end today. We
OL,14,Fcall for immediate action, clear
OL,15,Faccountability and real change, not
OL,16,Fsimply reassurances that 'lessons have
OL,17,Fbeen learned'.
OL,26,@qD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,F"The public deserves systems capable
OL,7,Fof identifying escalating risk,
OL,8,Fprotecting the vulnerable and
OL,9,Fpreventing acts of mass violence."
OL,11,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,12,Fthe report was "harrowing", and
OL,13,Fpledged his "total determination to
OL,14,Fmake the changes across the entire
OL,15,Fstate that is so clearly necessary to
OL,16,Fhonour the victims".
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@bO]tD@POUtD@ZO]uD@MOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FIn his report, comprising two volumes
OL,7,Fwith a total of 763 pages and setting
OL,8,Fout 67 recommendations, Sir Adrian
OL,9,Fsaid there was a "fundamental failure"
OL,10,Fby any organisation, or multi-agency
OL,11,Farrangement, to take ownership of the
OL,12,Frisk AR posed.
OL,14,FSpeaking at Liverpool Town Hall as the
OL,15,Freport was published, Sir Adrian said:
OL,16,F"I have no doubt that if appropriate
OL,17,Fprocedures had been in place and if
OL,18,Fsensible steps had been taken by the
OL,19,Fagencies and AR's parents, this
OL,20,Fdreadful event would not have happened.
OL,26,@qD@ROUqD@fO]xD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,F"It could have been and it should have
OL,7,Fbeen prevented."
OL,9,FSir Adrian said the failure, at an
OL,10,Forganisational and individual level,
OL,11,Fto "stand up and accept
OL,12,Fresponsibility" for managing the risk
OL,13,Fthe killer posed was a "frankly
OL,14,Fdepressing ` and therefore urgent `
OL,15,Fmatter requiring Government attention".
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@PO]tD@OO]uD@XOUwD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FHe said: "Far too often, AR's 'case'
OL,7,Fwas passed from one public sector
OL,8,Fagency to another in an inappropriate
OL,9,Fmerry-go-round of referrals,
OL,10,Fassessments, case-closures and 'hand-
OL,11,Foffs'."
OL,13,FChairman of the Southport Inquiry Sir
OL,14,FAdrian Fulford published the first
OL,15,Fphase of the report after a nine-week
OL,16,Finquiry.
OL,18,FSolicitor Nicola Ryan-Donnelly from
OL,19,FFletchers, representing 22 children
OL,20,Finjured in the attack, said the report
OL,21,Fmade for "disturbing reading".
OL,26,@nD@JOUsD@GO]}D@JOU}D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FSir Adrian said the teenager's
OL,7,Fparents, Alphonse Rudakubana and
OL,8,FLaetitia Muzayire, had "created
OL,9,Fsignificant obstructions" to
OL,10,Fengagement with him by various
OL,11,Fagencies and failed to stand up to his
OL,12,Fbehaviour and set boundaries, as well
OL,13,Fas failing to report a clear
OL,14,Fescalation in his risk.
OL,16,FHe said: "If AR's parents had done
OL,17,Fwhat they morally ought to have done,
OL,18,FAR would not have been at liberty to
OL,19,Fconduct the attack and it would not
OL,20,Ftherefore have occurred."
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@YO]xD@JOU|D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39515
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FBut he said it should have been
OL,7,F"obvious" to those in a position to
OL,8,Fact that AR was not being "effectively
OL,9,Fparented".
OL,11,FBoth the killer's parents, who moved
OL,12,Fto the UK from Rwanda, gave evidence
OL,13,Fto the inquiry from remote locations.
OL,15,FHis mother told the hearing: "There
OL,16,Fare many things that Alphonse and I
OL,17,Fwish we had done differently, anything
OL,18,Fthat might have prevented the horrific
OL,19,Fevent.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@IO]pD@[OUqD@IO]wD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39516
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FSir Adrian said AR had "clearly
OL,7,Frevealed the extreme danger that he
OL,8,Fpresented to others" more than four
OL,9,Fyears before his attack, when he went
OL,10,Fto his former school, the Range High
OL,11,FSchool in Formby, armed with a kitchen
OL,12,Fknife and a hockey stick and attacked
OL,13,Fa student.
OL,15,FThe inquiry chairman said the incident
OL,16,Fin December 2019, for which the
OL,17,Fteenager received a 10-month referral
OL,18,Forder, was a "watershed event" and
OL,19,Fshould have led agencies to conclude
OL,20,Fhe posed a "high risk of harm to
OL,21,Fothers".
OL,26,@nD@XOUpD@TO]zD@NOUzD@^O]|D@LOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G16/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39517
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FThe inquiry heard between 2019 and
OL,7,F2024, he was referred to anti-terror
OL,8,Fprogramme Prevent three times, but the
OL,9,Freferrals were closed.
OL,11,FHe purchased a number of weapons,
OL,12,Fincluding three machetes, online as
OL,13,Fwell as ingredients he used to make
OL,14,Fthe poison ricin.
OL,16,FSir Adrian said as time passed,
OL,17,Finteraction between AR and
OL,18,Forganisations became "at best,
OL,19,Fsomething of a token".
OL,26,@zD@VOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G17/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39518
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FHe said: "They were unaware of his
OL,7,Fcontinuing chilling internet
OL,8,Fpreoccupations and his accumulation of
OL,9,Flethal weapons, as well as the
OL,10,Fingredients for a lethal poison."
OL,12,FSir Adrian said "degrading, violent
OL,13,Fand misogynistic material" viewed
OL,14,Fonline by AR fed his "already
OL,15,Funhealthy fascination with violence".
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@aO]tD@QOUuD@ZO]vD@VOUwD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G18/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39519
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1776280294
OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FDownloads including an al Qaeda
OL,7,Ftraining manual, a history of Nazi
OL,8,FGermany and documents on wars in
OL,9,FRwanda, Sri Lanka, Somalia and South
OL,10,FSudan, were discovered on tablets
OL,11,Fbelonging to the killer after his
OL,12,Fattack.
OL,14,FThe inquiry chairman said the lack of
OL,15,Fexploration of his "online life" was a
OL,16,F"significant failure" which prevented
OL,17,Fagencies from identifying and
OL,18,Faddressing his risk.
OL,26,@wD@TOUwD@`O]xD@AOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G19/21
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
