OL,3,CSouthport lawyer 'will publicly name
OL,4,Cthose who failed to stop attack'
OL,6,FHe recommended that the second phase
OL,7,Fof the inquiry should consider
OL,8,Fabilities to restrict or monitor
OL,9,Faccess to the internet of children if
OL,10,Fthey pose a risk to others.
OL,12,FSir Adrian also said agencies failed
OL,13,Fto recognise that his diagnosis of
OL,14,Fautism spectrum disorder
OL,15,F"significantly increased the risk that
OL,16,Fhe posed" and there was a "repeated
OL,17,Ftendency" to excuse his behaviour on
OL,18,Fthe basis of his autism.
